Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. You must be Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we'll be sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your elder sister,\Nand you're my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we get along, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A crime in reality♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪For Heaven's sake♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Accepts any fake♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♪And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Won't take it at all, I get sick♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A girl looking back♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Casts the miracle into the instant world♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Did you lie♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Did you lie♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Spit the venom♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:02:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I know why♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've found a game of ecstasy♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Red Criminal gets life♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've never been in love♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪We will fly♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Someday I won't be crying♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,CONSPIRACY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not undo the Red String.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want all available fighters here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened just now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let me go!\N-Gemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto and Kyoka are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We eliminated all Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Naomi, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, do not tell anyone\Nwhat you witnessed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Our safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll report Naomi's\Ndisappearance as killed in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed in action?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order from the Major General.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Gemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The mission is still ongoing.\NDo not wander off on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki. I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi seems injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma, I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, look after Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi was strong and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Loss is inevitable as long as\Nwe're a member of the OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only do our best to cope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cursed Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When you die, you can't slack off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A member of OSF...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it worse, Yuito saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a word will get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,NEW MESSAGE. DO YOU WISH TO PLAY IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told Naomi died in the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our dear Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't turn down the recruitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We left Naomi in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We were wrong about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was foolish to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, do not contact us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to report what happened to Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran took Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For Naomi to become human again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we must rely on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They will not kill Naomi right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She can become human again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you want me to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand what happened to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,yet you doubt my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you managed to get her back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,she will be terminated as an Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You must keep this incident a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, not just Naomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,even your life would be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they would
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,actually kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not trust the people of New Himuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You were there when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess telling you shouldn't\Nbe considered treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran took Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the OSF hiding from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this has something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I kept it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ampoule?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I found them by the abandoned tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be some sort of drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It has the mark of Seiran City on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be best if you didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that monster was Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-But I...\N-Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this might be fancy words to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but I want to help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are fancy words indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I appreciate it./
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost contact with him after\Nthey rushed him to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a volunteer just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to the same training school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But because of my family, people treated me\Nlike I was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Nagi treated me like a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that wasn't very normal after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say he was overly friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't have come this far without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not concerned about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When you push yourself too hard\Nin a battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you put your comrades in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not fighting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, you still have those\Nin the Kyoka Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a blind spot\Nfor the surveillance system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The preparation is almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What about our plan to take down OSF?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This country will be ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An alarm of unprecedented scale\Nhas been announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The location is centered\Naround a ten-kilometer radius
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Kunad Highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All soldiers of the OSF will be deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We've issued an evacuation order\Nto citizens of the Suoh capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry up!\N-Get to the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-They are overreacting.\N-The monsters are in Kunad, not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to the shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All members, deploy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hinokami Platoon, move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakaki Platoon, move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka, see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Watch your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Gemma going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Others came in large numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He was assigned to command\Na special platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kageru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. I'm simply excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. I'll follow Captain Seto's order\Nand not overdo myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't die before I get Naomi back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're discharged, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that, Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Private Nagi Karman
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,reporting to duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're glad you're back.\NEveryone was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Going back into action\Nright after his discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The army can be really harsh sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to stretch my limbs anyway.\NI'll take this as my rehab therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's save the chitchat for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, are you sure you'd be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My injury is almost healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I meant what happened to Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still not over Naomi's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't keep sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's weird\Nthat she was turned into an Other...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean she turned into an Other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't joke about something so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Kasane heard it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We will continue to fight the Others\Nfor the sake of New Himuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be tough,\Nbut we must keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We should head to the forecast locations now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We've met a few of them before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but not in this number.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We could get off work early\Nif there weren't many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it's too quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the surrounding area?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is different from the forecast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could there be an error?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll confirm the Other attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru? What's wrong, Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto, please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get a hold of Captain Kyoka either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a jamming signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, we've been surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are OSF soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Were there other platoons
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that were sent to this location?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma, what is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We could go home early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare give us more work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma, what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto, I can't believe you've done\Nsuch a horrible experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop pretending now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka Travers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can handle\Ntwo Septentrions at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka, what is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take care of these soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-Run while you...\N-If I'm your opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,will you still be as confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka, you've come at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I'll handle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain field!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sclerokinesis, electrokinesis, and aerokinesis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He can copy people's powers\Nand use them as his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A brain eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the mastermind behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This country...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka has lied to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what happened to Naomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Naomi?\N-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Himuka Government is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Gemma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I don't need to let fate dictate me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.96,0:22:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Because I believe that I can rewrite it♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.67,0:22:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.71,0:23:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪What's waiting for us at the world's end♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Forever eternal, keep the fire going♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Who can shake us♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Who can define us♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪It's nothing less than our story♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,RED STRINGS
